Whats Doggo Api?

DoggoApi its a page dedicated to show information about the breeds of dogs from all over the world. We are compromised with our users, and their knowledge about the man's best friends, dogs. Whether you want to make the right choice to pick the ideal new member of your family, or just want to learn about these wonderfull animals, you will find all the information you need here, on DoggoApi.

How does DoggoApi work?

All of the information showed on this page is extracted from the dogs API, a place where people and companies can extract information related with breeds of dogs. We also count with our own data base, which we use to store the breeds created bu our users.

Technologies used

In order to create this aplication we have used some intresting technologies that we would like to share with you
